nodes.text: Brian Drummond (born August 10, 1969) is a Canadian voice actor who provided the voice of Bobby in LEGO Star Wars: The Yoda Chronicles and Admiral Motti, Zeb and Watto in LEGO Star Wars: Droid Tales.
